@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qwqard(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(v0)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.51))
    v2 = 0.64
    v0 = (v1 / wp.exp((v2 + 0.43 / tmp + 0.70)))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
